https://www.youtube.com/watch?v=ZpR1W-NWnp4
https://tonyteaches.tech/django-nginx-uwsgi-tutorial/


 **INITIAL PYTHON-DJANGO CONF**

- python3 --version --> Python 3.8.5
- sudo apt-get install python3-venv
- python3 -m venv sl-env
- source sl-env/bin/activate (activate envirorment)
- pip install Django (or in my case: pip install -r requirements.txt)

 **INTERFACE GETWAY** 

sudo apt-get install python3.8-dev
sudo apt-get install gcc
pip install uwsgi

 **NGINX

- sudo apt-get install nginx
- nano /etc/nginx/sites-available/sl.conf --> add conf to this doc.
- sudo ln -s /etc/nginx/sites-available/sl.conf /etc/nginx/sites-enabled/

 ** settings.py CONFIG

 ** MAKE IT WORK ALL TOGETHER
uwsgi --socket shoppinglist.sock --module shoppinglist.wsgi --chmod-socket=666

 **DEPLOY FOR PROD
ps aux 
sudo ln -s /home/liset/sl_app_NGINX_uWSGI/shoppinglist/sl_uwsgi.ini /home/liset/sl_app_NGINX_uWSGI/sl-env/vassals

EMPEROR
uwsgi --emperor /home/liset/sl_app_NGINX_uWSGI/sl-env/vassals --uid www-data --gid www-data

